Package: pkgraph
Type: Package
Title: Fancy Graphs with GGPlot
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Philipp", "Kollenda", email = "p.kollenda@vu.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package uses best practices from data visualizations to create appealing graphs with 
    a coherent theme. Inspiration comes from VU Data Visualization Course, BBC Cookbook and Guardian Visualisations,
    the book Data Visualizations by Kieran Healy and the website chrisbail.net.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4.2)
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Imports: tidyverse, cowplot, scales
URL: https://github.com/pkollenda/pkgraph
BugReports: https://github.com/pkollenda/pkgraph/issues
